{
  "chapter": 79,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十九回 恐怖的决斗。孙老先生向李寻欢揭示怜花宝典的来龙去脉：王怜花将毕生心血所著的怜花宝典托付给李寻欢保管，并希望他代寻传人。李寻欢当时恰好不在，王怜花遂将宝典交给了林诗音。孙小红透露其二叔受王怜花之托，一直在暗中守护李寻欢。李寻欢得知林诗音从未将宝典转交给他，心中震动。随后场景转至陋巷，孙驼子的小店中发现一只被齐腕砍断的手——孙驼子已被害。门后留有血掌印，李寻欢和孙小红意识到这是上官金虹设下的圈套。二人毅然进入，发现地下室中铁传甲正与中原八义成员及一群黄衣人殊死搏斗。铁传甲为偿还旧债，甘愿以身赴死，最终倒在公孙雨的刀锋之下。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "他为什么想烧了它？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为那上面不但有他的武功心法，也记载着他的下毒术、易容术、苗人放蛊、波斯传来的慑心术……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么样一本书若是落在不肖之徒的手里，后果岂非不堪设想？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那的确是后患无穷。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这是他一生心血所聚，他也不舍得将之毁于一旦，所以，他远赴海外之前，就将这本书交给了一个他认为最可靠的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他将这本秘笈交给谁了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "交给了你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "普天之下，除了小李探花外，还有谁是最可靠的人呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他将这本怜花宝典交付给你，不但要你替他保存，还想要你替他找个天资高、心术好的弟子，作为他的衣钵传人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这件事我却连一点都不知道。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你那时恰巧出去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十三年前……不错，那时我到关外去了一趟，回来时又遇伏受了重伤，若不是龙啸云仗义相救，我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花虽未见着你，却见到了林姑娘，那时他远游在即，沈大侠已在海口等着他，他自然不能停留，所以就将那怜花宝典交给了林姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事不知前辈是从哪里听到的是不是很可靠？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝对可靠。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事就是我二叔说的，王老前辈到兴云庄……不，到李园去见林姑娘的时候，我二叔就在外面等着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自从那天之后，一直到现在，我二叔就从未离开过那地方一步！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他就是受了王怜花的托付，在那里监视着我？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花既然肯将那么重要的东西交给你，就绝不会对你不放心，只不过，他对你的武功还不大信任，生怕有人听到消息，会去夺书，所以才会要老二留在那里，到了必要时，也好助你一臂之力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我二叔当年游侠江湖间，曾经被王老前辈救过一命，他这人最是恩怨分明，王老前辈要他做的事，他的确可说是万死不辞。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但后来却在无意中听到林姑娘并没有将那怜花宝典转交给你，所以你出关之后，他更不放心，更不肯离开一步了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "受人之托，忠人之事，孙二侠不愧为王老前辈的好朋友，只不过……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孙二侠又怎会知道林姑娘未曾将怜花宝典转交给我？这件事连我自己都不知道。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连你都不知道，我又怎么会知道？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花不但有杀人的本事，也有救人的手段，中年后医道更精，的确可说已有生死人，肉白骨的功力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙小云是林姑娘的亲生儿子，一个做母亲的若是为了儿子确是不惜做任何事的，所以，我想……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan_mu_qin",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢母亲",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这是你姨妈的女儿，你姨妈到很远很远的地方去了，所以她从今天开始，就要住在我们家里。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan_mu_qin",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢母亲",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你总是埋怨自己没有妹妹，现在我替你找了个妹妹来了，你一定要对她好些，绝不能让她生气。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_nian_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "幼年林诗音",
      "listener": "char_young_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他为什么没有眼睛？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_nian_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "幼年李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_young_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你喜不喜欢替他装上对眼睛？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在还没有到吃晚饭的时候，客人还不会上门，不知道二叔现在干什么？是不是又在抹桌子？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知道这只手是谁的？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他的人呢……他的人呢？……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "上官金虹也早已算准了你要到这里来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他知道你绝不会先到兴云庄去，因为你不愿再见到龙啸云，所以你心里无论多么急，也一定会先到二叔店里来瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这一切，正都是为你设下的圈套。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "所以你绝不能走进这扇门。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我没关系，上官金虹并不急着要杀我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "所以你可以进去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我非进去不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "看来你还不如上官金虹那么了解我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他苦心设下这圈套，就因为他知道我也是非进去不可的，就算有人已将我的两条腿砍断，我爬也要爬进去！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "铁传甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们退，我挡住他们……快退！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_weng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "翁大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能退，我们死也要把他带出去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_weng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "翁大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人是我们的，除了我们外，谁也不能动他一根手指，谁也不能……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "铁传甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们真的不走？……你们若全都死了，又怎能将我带走？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi_mang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们全都死了，也要将你的鬼魂带走！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "铁传甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若是死在你们手上呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi_mang_ren",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的事本就和我们无关，我们本就是为了你来的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yu",
      "speaker_name": "公孙雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中原八义若不能亲手取你的命，死不瞑目！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "铁传甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们只不过想亲手杀了我，这容易……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_chuan_jia",
      "speaker_name": "铁传甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在……我的债总可还清了吧！你们还不走？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    }
  ],
